OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely dry
OL,6,Fand mostly cloudy, with a few isolated
OL,7,Fshowers, this evening. The cloud
OL,8,Fbreaking up to give occasional clear
OL,9,Fspells overnight. Breezy and mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FLargely dry with sunny spells
OL,12,Fduring the morning. Cloud increasing
OL,13,Fto bring outbreaks of showery rain,
OL,14,Fperhaps locally heavy, by late
OL,15,Fafternoon and evening. Feeling warm in
OL,16,Fsunshine. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
