OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FSunny
OL,6,Fspells and showers Saturday. Drier and
OL,7,Fsunnier with winds easing Sunday.
OL,8,FCloudier on Monday with showers
OL,9,Fspreading inland from coastal areas.
OL,10,FFeeling cooler, especially along
OL,11,Fwindward coastal districts.
